verbose_text: Overexpression of the lymphangiogenic growth factor VEGF-C increased lymphatic sprouting, as the number and cumulative length of lymphatic sprouts increased by 247 +/-15% and 406 +/-29%, respectively (n = 50, P < 0.001) (XREF_FIG).
evidence: Overexpression of the lymphangiogenic growth factor VEGF-C
